'''凯莉·玛丽莎·华盛顿'''<ref name="birth">{{cite web|url=http://pastthepen.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/nnamdi-kerry-washington-wedding-certificate.jpg|publisher=E! Online|date=July 3, 2013|accessdate=September 26, 2013|title=Kerry Washington wedding certificate|archive-date=2015-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150724215831/https://pastthepen.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/nnamdi-kerry-washington-wedding-certificate.jpg|dead-url=no}}</ref>（{{lang-en|Kerry Marisa Washington}}，{{bd|1977年|1月31日||}}<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/learning/general/onthisday/20090131.html|title=Today's Highlights in History: January 31|date=January 31, 2009|accessdate=August 6, 2009|publisher=''New York Times''|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304195556/http://www.nytimes.com/learning/general/onthisday/20090131.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>），美国影视女演员。自2012年以来，凯莉出演[[ABC|ABC]]电视剧《[[丑闻_(电视剧)|丑闻]]》得到了公众的广泛认可，她在[[珊达·莱梅斯|珊达·莱梅斯]]的这部剧中饰演[[美国总统|美国总统]]的危机管理专家奥利维娅·波普<ref>{{cite web|last=Bricker|first=Tierney|url=http://blog.zap2it.com/frominsidethebox/2011/05/abc-picks-up-charlies-angels-good-christian-belles-and-ten-more.html|title=ABC picks up 'Charlie's Angels,' 'Good Christian Belles' and ten more|date=May 13, 2011|accessdate=October 1, 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120505020628/http://blog.zap2it.com/frominsidethebox/2011/05/abc-picks-up-charlies-angels-good-christian-belles-and-ten-more.html|archivedate=2012年5月5日}}</ref>。凭借她的角色，凯莉两次提名[[黄金时段艾美奖|黄金时段艾美奖]]最佳电视剧女主角和[[美国演员工会奖|美国演员工会奖]]电视戏剧类最佳女演员以及一次[[金球奖|金球奖]]最佳电视剧女主角。

凯莉亦因在电影《[[灵魂歌王|灵魂歌王]]》出演[[雷·查尔斯|雷·查尔斯]]的妻子德拉·比亚·罗宾逊闻名，此外她还饰演了《[[末代独裁|末代独裁]]》（2006）[[伊迪·阿敏|伊迪·阿敏]]的妻子凯，饰演了《[[神奇四侠|神奇四侠]]》[[神奇四侠_(电影)|2005年]]和[[神奇四侠：银魔现身|2007年电影]]中[[石头人|石头人]]的爱人艾莉西亚·马斯特，饰演了[[昆汀·塔伦蒂诺|昆汀·塔伦蒂诺]]电影《[[被解放的姜戈|被解放的姜戈]]》（2013）中姜戈的妻子布鲁姆希尔达·冯·夏福特。她还出演了广受好评的独立电影《我们的歌》（2000）、《死亡女孩》（2006）、《母与子》（2009）、《夜晚吞噬了我们》（2010）。

2014年4月，《[[时代_(杂志)|时代]]》杂志在一年一度的[[时代百大人物|时代百大人物]]评选中，将凯莉列入“世界最具影响人的人物<ref>{{cite web|url=http://time.com/70800/kerry-washington-2014-time-100/|title=Kerry Washington 2014 Time|accessdate=April 26, 2014|archive-date=2014-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140425150724/http://time.com/70800/kerry-washington-2014-time-100/|dead-url=no}}</ref>”。

== 早年生活 ==
凯莉生于[[纽约|纽约]][[布朗克斯|布朗克斯]]区，母亲瓦莱丽是教授和教育顾问，父亲厄尔·华盛顿是房地产经纪人。父亲是[[南卡罗来纳州|南卡罗来纳州]]和[[布鲁克林|布鲁克林]]的[[非裔美国人|非裔美国人]]<ref name=elc>{{Cite news|last=Stein|first=Ruthe|title=Washington's 'Mother' instinct|date=2010-05-09|url=http://articles.sfgate.com/2010-05-09/entertainment/20889631_1_sundance-film-festival-first-feature-film-kerry-washington|accessdate=2010-09-21|work=The San Francisco Chronicle|archive-date=2010-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100625043439/http://articles.sfgate.com/2010-05-09/entertainment/20889631_1_sundance-film-festival-first-feature-film-kerry-washington|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="filmr">[http://www.filmreference.com/film/35/Kerry-Washington.html Kerry Washington Biography (1977)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.filmreference.com/film/35/Kerry-Washington.html |date=20160303234621 }} Film Reference</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Collins|first=Lauren|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2004/10/24/fashion/24NITE.html|title=Kerry Washington: Politics and Shabu Shabu|work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]|date=October 24, 2004|accessdate=November 16, 2012|archive-date=2015-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150528070045/http://www.nytimes.com/2004/10/24/fashion/24NITE.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，母亲出生于曼哈顿。华盛顿表示，她的母亲有着“牙买加人的混血背景，所以她不仅有部分英格兰人、苏格兰人和本土美国人的血统，还是加勒比海非洲黑奴的后裔”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/lifestyle/-SO-Who-Knew--Washington-Connects-The-Dots_12733464|title=SO Who Knew? Washington Connects The Dots|date=October 14, 2012|accessdate=November 16, 2012|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612142534/http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/lifestyle/-SO-Who-Knew--Washington-Connects-The-Dots_12733464|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Powell|first=Kevin|title=Kerry Washington: Woman on Top|url=http://www.ebony.com/entertainment-culture/kerry-washington-woman-on-top-333#axzz2TammW85p|accessdate=May 17, 2013|newspaper=Ebony|date=May 9, 2013|archive-date=2013-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004234813/http://www.ebony.com/entertainment-culture/kerry-washington-woman-on-top-333#axzz2TammW85p|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Curtis|first=Nick|title=Kerry Washington on making Quentin Tarantino's Django Unchained|url=http://www.standard.co.uk/lifestyle/london-life/kerry-washington-on-making-quentin-tarantinos-django-unchained-8453865.html|accessdate=May 17, 2013|newspaper=Evening Standard|date=January 16, 2013|archive-date=2015-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150223084358/http://www.standard.co.uk/lifestyle/london-life/kerry-washington-on-making-quentin-tarantinos-django-unchained-8453865.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她的母親是[[美国国务卿|美国国务卿]][[克林·鲍威尔|克林·鲍威尔]] （Colin Powell）的表親<ref>{{cite news|last=Leive|first=Cindi|title=Kerry Washington Talks Her New Marriage, Scandal Style, and Her Real-Life Gladiators in Glamour's October Issue|url=http://www.glamour.com/entertainment/blogs/obsessed/2013/09/kerry-washington-glamour-inter.html|accessdate=November 14, 2013|newspaper=Glamour|date=September 3, 2013|archive-date=2013-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111102830/http://www.glamour.com/entertainment/blogs/obsessed/2013/09/kerry-washington-glamour-inter.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

凯莉于1994年在曼哈顿斯彭斯学校毕业，跟TADA！年轻人剧院青少年组演员登台<ref name="Kerry"/>。1998年她在[[乔治·华盛顿大学|乔治·华盛顿大学]]以人类学和社会学双学会的优等生成绩毕业<ref name="Kerry"/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://theybf.com/2012/10/15/inside-black-girls-rock-red-carpet-arrivals-what-you-can-expect-from-the-show|title=INSIDE Black Girls Rock! Red Carpet Arrivals & What You Can Expect From The Show|date=October 15, 2012|accessdate=November 16, 2012|archive-date=2012-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121117131556/http://theybf.com/2012/10/15/inside-black-girls-rock-red-carpet-arrivals-what-you-can-expect-from-the-show|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。她还就读于纽约市的迈克尔·霍华德工作室<ref name="Kerry">{{cite web|title=About Kerry Washington|url=http://movies.yahoo.com/person/kerry-washington/biography.html|work=Yahoo! Movies|accessdate=1 October 2012|archive-date=2013-03-09|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6EzXKF156?url=http://movies.yahoo.com/person/kerry-washington/biography.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 私生活 ==
