凯莉于2004年10月至2007年3月间与演员[[大卫·莫斯科|大卫·莫斯科]]展开感情交往<ref>{{cite news|title=Kerry Washington: Dating Scared Me|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20044322,00.html|accessdate=July 3, 2013|magazine=''People''|date=July 7, 2007|archive-date=2014-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141102102924/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20044322,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年6月24日，凯莉在[[爱达荷州|爱达荷州]]黑利嫁给了[[NFL|NFL]]球员[[纳姆迪·阿索穆加|纳姆迪·阿索穆加]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Kerry Washington Weds Nnamdi Asomugha|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20714709,00.html|accessdate=July 4, 2013|magazine=''People''|date=July 3, 2013|archive-date=2015-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150311233528/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20714709,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-207_162-57592284/kerry-washington-weds-pro-athlete-nnamdi-asomugha/|title=Kerry Washington weds pro athlete Nnamdi Asomugha|date=3 July 2013|work=[[CBS_News|CBS News]]|accessdate=8 July 2013|archive-date=2013-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130707164124/http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-207_162-57592284/kerry-washington-weds-pro-athlete-nnamdi-asomugha|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.upi.com/blog/2013/07/05/Nnamdi-Asomugha-secretly-weds-Scandal-star-Kerry-Washington/2651373040709/|title=Nnamdi Asomugha secretly weds 'Scandal' star Kerry Washington - UPI.com|last=Lee|first=Caroline|work=upi.com|year=2013|accessdate=July 8, 2013|archive-date=2013-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130709031930/http://www.upi.com/blog/2013/07/05/Nnamdi-Asomugha-secretly-weds-Scandal-star-Kerry-Washington/2651373040709|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他们的女儿伊莎贝尔·阿玛拉奇于2014年4月21日出生<ref name=washington_baby>{{cite web|last=Blumm|first=K.C.|title=Kerry Washington Welcomes Daughter Isabelle Amarachi|url=http://celebritybabies.people.com/2014/05/02/kerry-washington-welcomes-daughter-isabelle-amarachi-nnamdi-asomugha/|publisher=People|accessdate=2 May 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140504010310/http://celebritybabies.people.com/2014/05/02/kerry-washington-welcomes-daughter-isabelle-amarachi-nnamdi-asomugha/|archive-date=2014-05-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

凯莉通常会保留她所饰演角色的道具，作为纪念，如衣服或角色所住房子的家具<ref>[http://www.craveonline.com/filmtv/articles/04647599/we_love_kerry_washington.html We Love Kerry Washington] {{Wayback|url=http://www.craveonline.com/filmtv/articles/04647599/we_love_kerry_washington.html |date=20070707113651 }} Crave Online.</ref>。

2013年5月19日，凯莉回到母校[[乔治华盛顿大学|乔治华盛顿大学]]发表毕业演讲，并被授予美术学[[名誉学位|名誉学位]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Alyssa|first=Newcomb|title=Kerry Washington: 'Scandal' Star Shares Memories From Her College Years|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/kerry-washington-scandal-star-honorary-doctorate-george-washington/story?id=19211377#.UZo0zKLVCjQ|accessdate=May 20, 2013|newspaper=ABC News|date=May 19, 2013|archive-date=2015-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150227102952/http://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/kerry-washington-scandal-star-honorary-doctorate-george-washington/story?id=19211377#.UZo0zKLVCjQ|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Kerry Washington at GWU commencement: Grads must be ‘heroes of own lives’|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/reliable-source/wp/2013/05/19/kerry-washington-at-gwu-commencement-grads-must-be-heroes-of-own-lives/|accessdate=May 20, 2013|newspaper=washingtonpost|date=May 19, 2013|archive-date=2015-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150227105156/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/reliable-source/wp/2013/05/19/kerry-washington-at-gwu-commencement-grads-must-be-heroes-of-own-lives/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

